Package: libcommrat-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends},
         libsertial-dev, libreflect-cpp-dev, rack
Description: CommRaT - C++20 real-time communication framework (dev headers)
 Combines RACK's TiMS IPC message service with SeRTial's zero-allocation
 serialization. Provides compile-time type-safe messaging, module framework,
 and real-time capable publish/subscribe patterns.
